# Safe example file for local setup documentation.
# This file is safe to commit because it contains placeholders only.
# Real .env files must never be committed.
#
# SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY or SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY must never be used in browser code.
# Browser/public keys are only acceptable with strict RLS and least-privilege policies.
# Future core Postgres credentials must also stay server-side only.

